{"履修期": "春学期", "主な教授言語": "英語", "授業目的": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">The\nobjectives of this course are:</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">1.\nTo help students acquire English presentation/discussion skills</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">2.\nTo help students present their ideas clearly and effectively</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">3.\nTo help students think independently and critically </span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">4.\nTo provide students with opportunities to give English presentations on various\ntopics </span></p>\n\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"ｍｓ=\"roman',serif;mso-fareast-font-family:'ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;\"=\"明朝';mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">5.\nTo help students become better audience members</span>", "到達目標": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">1.\nStudents will develop speech-building strategies.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">2.\nStudents will acquire better communication skills.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">3.\nStudents will familiarize themselves with presentation/discussion techniques.</span></p>\n\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"ｍｓ=\"roman',serif;mso-fareast-font-family:'ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;\"=\"明朝';mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">4.\nStudents will become more confident public speakers.</span>", "特記事項": "", "関連科目": "<span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"roman',serif;mso-fareast-font-family:'times\" roman\";mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;\"=\"roman';mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">English Skills C\n(01-02)</span>", "授業の概要・背景": "", "授業方法": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"roman',serif;mso-fareast-font-family:'times\" roman\";\"=\"roman';'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">1. This course will be conducted in\nEnglish only and English will be the means of communication between the\nstudents and the instructor.&nbsp; (Students\nwill also be expected to communicate with one another in English.)</span></p>\n\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"roman',serif;mso-fareast-font-family:'times\" roman\";mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;\"=\"roman';mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">2.&nbsp;\nStudents are encouraged to actively participate in class discussions,\nboth independently and collaboratively, in order to enhance their competence\nand confidence in English and also to create a better learning environment for\nall.&nbsp;</span>", "トピック": {"第1回": ["<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"920\">\n <tbody><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes;height:15.0pt;\">\n  <td width=\"641\" style=\"width:480.9pt;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom-width:1pt;border-bottom-color:windowtext;border-right-width:1pt;border-right-color:windowtext;background:rgb(204,255,204);padding:0mm 5.4pt;height:15pt;\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:;\">Course\n  Description &amp; Introduction</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n</div>", ""], "第2回": ["<span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"roman',serif;mso-fareast-font-family:'times\" roman\";mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;\"=\"roman';mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">Unit 1</span>", ""], "第3回": ["<span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"roman',serif;mso-fareast-font-family:'times\" roman\";mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;\"=\"roman';mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">Unit 2</span>", ""], "第4回": ["<span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"roman',serif;m